  "prompt": "How do I know if a shy guy likes me?",
  "response": "It can sometimes be challenging to discern if a shy person has romantic feelings for you, but there are several signs that might indicate their interest:\n\n1. **Body Language**: \n   - **Eye Contact**: Although shy individuals may avoid prolonged eye contact, if he frequently glances at you or seems to look your way often, it might be a sign of interest.\n   - **Nervousness**: He may fidget, blush, or appear anxious when around you.\n   - **Mirroring**: He might subtly mirror your actions and movements.\n\n2. **Behavior**:\n   - **Initiative**: Despite his shyness, he may try to initiate conversations or find reasons to be near you.\n   - **Attentiveness**: He listens carefully when you talk and remembers details about you, even small things.\n   - **Supportive**: He offers help or support without being asked.\n\n3. **Communication**:\n   - **Indirect Communication**: He might send messages through mutual friends or use social media to engage indirectly.\n   - **Texting**: He might feel more comfortable expressing himself through texts or online chats.\n\n4. **Social Interactions**:\n   - **Friends and Family**: His friends or family might drop hints or tease him about you.\n   - **Jealousy**: He might look uncomfortable if you are speaking to other potential romantic interests.\n\n5. **Personal Effort**:\n   - **Appearance**: He may put extra effort into his appearance when he knows he will see you.\n   - **Special Treatment**: He treats you differently compared to others, often in a positive, caring manner.\n\nWhile these signs can suggest that a shy guy likes you, it's important to consider them in context and not jump to conclusions. Being direct and open in your own communication can also help clarify feelings and intentions.",
